船導致破產的人沒有兩樣，不勝唏噓。</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:44:27.000Z","msg":"其實只要一個合適既 財務管理 我唔認為香港人會咁傻 將所有錢 都放曬落去Vtuber 嗰度 但都多謝你提提大家唔好咁做"},{"pid":"c1958f4be5a172f33f213866f2283059b5ac40c1","tid":2374450,"uid":305269,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TyVtkd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyVtkd8.jpg&h=b5653f48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c08479f282bc08294876f093bfc80983c0149e4","tid":2374450,"uid":350651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1958f4be5a172f33f213866f2283059b5ac40c1","tid":2374450,"uid":305269,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TyVtkd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyVtkd8.jpg&h=b5653f48&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"Shark !!!!"},{"pid":"d10300a46dc383efecdb2bdafe012830c9a21a9f","tid":2374450,"uid":54485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce93f868d0cc8ecbe6bfc28d2ac662a1bb6d08fb","tid":2374450,"uid":350651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b0a5b422041382063300bf4517b465608986103","tid":2374450,"uid":54485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a270a17b21ea23477438da04d6aea23508d096","tid":2374450,"uid":350651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"你要明白我地e d無女既幸福 就係咁黎 男人就係咁簡單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"拎舊錢改變下自己咪有囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:40:33.000Z","msg":"有時你要明白點解e家vtuber 咁 受歡迎 係因為係e個工作壓力 社會壓力 家庭壓力下既一班人 係e個疫情無得出街 當佢地對人生沒有意義時 係屋企好無聊 或者對疫情好驚好徬徨  Vtuber既歡笑聲 佢地對你既關心反而成為一個 救贖 。 我都一樣被Vtuber 救贖左我既心 令我重新振作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:57:06.000Z","msg":"理解唔到<br />\n早日得救"},{"pid":"c8feb26268f96424c1b5d757e9bc5af1c48804e6","tid":2374450,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9